                <li><strong>0–100 km/h:</strong> ~5.6 seconds</li>
                <li><strong>Transmission:</strong> 6-Speed Manual</li>
                <li><strong>Fuel Type:</strong> Petrol</li>
                <li><strong>Market Value:</strong> $3,000 – $4,000 (Used)</li>
